Flextech chief Luard says no plans to quit . Britain ' s Flextech Plc denied on Monday weekend press reports that its chief executive Roger Luard was to leave the company . Denying a Sunday Express report Luard said : " I remain committed to Flextech and have no plans to leave . I fully intend to be involved in Flextech ' s continued growth and development " . Flextech ' s share price had fallen 19 pence to 634 before Luard ' s assurance came . It was last traded at 636p at 1450 GMT . - - London Newsroom + 44 171 542 4366 
